						               													<description>Welcome to a world of floating castles, airships and dragons! Castles float by power of a mystic stone called Dragonite. Merchants and regents maneuver the skies in elegant airships. Dragon Lords dominate the clouds.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In MEGA Mini Dragons, players choose a dragon and interact with the merchants and regents who come to the valley to trade or beg protection. They come bearing dazzling gems, precious Dragonite or even a rare dragon egg - all being the preferred currency of the Dragon Lords. Gems are crafted into precious items like rings, necklaces and scepters. Eggs are hatched and the Dragonite hoarded. Dragon Riders accumulate these items to elevate their status in dragon society.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;MEGA Mini Dragons is a 1-4 player, strategic board game of resource management with exclusive dragon meeples. Each turn, new merchant cards are dealt beneath the floating castle cards. Players spontaneously decide to which castle they send their Dragon Rider. If two or more players choose the same castle, the player with the higher status sends the contenders to a different castle. Castles and merchants offer different resources and crafting choices. Every turn, Dragon Council cards are dealt face down, which dictate item values at the end of the game. Players may choose to spend an action to sneak a peek at values, or even bribe a Council member - and switch a value card for one that pays proper respect to their pile of dragon loot!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Dragon Lords, take to the skies! The merchants come bearing gifts. Royalty from distant lands throw themselves at our mercy. The world is ripe. Can your Dragon Rider scale the peaks of dragon society in the clouds? Jump on your dragon in the next game of Mega Mini Dragons to find out!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
